<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7f00ff, #e100ff);
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  margin: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.container {
  width: 80%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  padding: 60px 40px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  border-radius: 15px;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  animation: zoomIn 1.5s ease-out;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.container::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -50%;
  left: -50%;
  width: 200%;
  height: 200%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), transparent);
  animation: floatBackground 12s infinite ease-in-out;
  z-index: 0;
}

.logo {
  width: 120px;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  display: block;
  z-index: 1;
  position: relative;
}

h1 {
  text-align: center;
  color: #0c0202;
  font-size: 3.5em;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  z-index: 1;
  position: relative;
  animation: glowingText 1.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

button {
  padding: 15px 30px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e2de2, #4a00e0);
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 1.5em;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <img src="../VoxView.png" alt="Logo" class=""Decoding Debate, Defining Discourse"">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Site VoxView!</h1>
            
            <h4>Decoding Debate, Defining Discourse</h4>
        </header>
        <main>
            <h2>Hello, user!</h2>
            <p>We are delighted to have you here. Explore our website to discover more about what we offer.</p>
            <button>Learn More</button>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Our Site. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>